h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, Tr\u01b0\u1edfng ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a VFF, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1ea3i H\u01b0\u1eddng cho bi\u1ebft h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t treo gi\u00f2 8 tr\u1eadn sau pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Duy M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hau ve Tang Tien co the bi treo gio 8 tran, phat 35 trieu dong hinh anh\" title=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 8 tr\u1eadn, ph\u1ea1t 35 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/hlv-le-thuy-hai-noi-gi-ve-an-phat-cua-bau-duc-voi-tang-tien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><em>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u 8 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 n\u1ed9p ph\u1ea1t 35 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng</em></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau h\u00e0nh vi v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Duy M\u1ea1nh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt b\u1eb1ng \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 t\u1edbi h\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u00eam \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a VFF. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, vi\u1ec7c T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t l\u00e0 v\u00ec ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a VFF \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Duy M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u 10/4, Tr\u01b0\u1edfng ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a VFF, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1ea3i H\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft: \"C\u0103n c\u1ee9 theo b\u00e1o c\u00e1o, b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn sau pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i, d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u1ecbu ch\u1ebf t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a kho\u1ea3n 2 \u0110i\u1ec1u 39 trong Quy \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a VFF (ph\u1ea1t ti\u1ec1n t\u1eeb 25-35 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng, treo gi\u00f2 5-8 tr\u1eadn). <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu \u00e1p m\u1ee9c 3 th\u00ec n\u1eb7ng qu\u00e1, c\u00f2n m\u1ee9c 1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea1i cho l\u00e0 h\u01a1i nh\u1eb9. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i c\u00f2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng 11/4\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng theo \u00f4ng H\u01b0\u1eddng, d\u00f9 ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 mua b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 song \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, c\u00f2n VFF v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 quy \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 vi ph\u1ea1m ph\u1ea3i chi tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 ti\u1ec1n ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1ebfu g\u00e2y h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng cho \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t treo gi\u00f2 8 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 n\u1ed9p ph\u1ea1t 30 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng\u00a0t\u1eeb Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF sau pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Anh H\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2017.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#081f2c;=\"\" mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1010","checkdouble":"183966"},{"date":"21:34 10/04","title":"HLV Tampines Rovers kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a SLNA","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/10/hlv-tampines-rovers-khong-phuc-chien-thang-cua-slna.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{marg