bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, doanh thu Arsenal c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd t\u0103ng m\u1ea1nh n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y k\u00ed h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng Adidas.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Arsenal l\u00e0 Puma. V\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 thu v\u1ec1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n n\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c \u1edf Anh.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doanh thu cua Arsenal hua hen tang manh neu bo Puma theo Adidas hinh anh\" title=\"Doanh thu c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n t\u0103ng m\u1ea1nh n\u1ebfu b\u1ecf Puma theo Adidas h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/ha-southampton-arsenal-san-bang-ky-luc-gan-60-nam-truoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec v\u1eady, Arsenal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00ed h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Puma. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi (2018-19). Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 m\u1edbi, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng Adidas.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c SportMail ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi ti\u1ebft. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Adidas \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi h\u01a1n 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a n\u1ebfu tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAdidas hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u1ea1nh tranh r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t v\u1edbi Nike n\u00ean h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf Premier League. T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ed1 1 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, Adidas \u0111ang t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u cho Man Utd v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a v\u1edbi Adidas, Arsenal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf Premier League, ch\u1ec9 sau Man Utd (75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a - Adidas) v\u00e0 Chelsea (60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a - Nike). M\u1ee9c thu t\u1eeb \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua 2 \u00f4ng l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c \u1edf Anh l\u00e0 Tottenham (30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a - Nike) v\u00e0 Man City (20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a - Nike).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Adidas, Arsenal c\u00f2n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c cho ph\u1ea7n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u1edf ph\u00eda tay \u00e1o. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 1 trong nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Premier League, gi\u00fap c\u00e1c CLB thu v\u1ec1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n nh\u1edd th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"999","checkdouble":"183935"},{"date":"14:37 10/04","title":"MU treo \u1ea3nh Messi lau gi\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/10/mu-treo-anh-messi-lau-giay-de-giao-duc-lua-tre.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opac