 \u00f4ng Tr\u1ea7n Anh T\u00fa (b\u1ea7u T\u00fa) \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed T\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c VPF \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung cho c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bau Tu kiem nhiem ghe Truong Ban dieu hanh giai dau.\" title=\"B\u1ea7u T\u00fa ki\u00eam nhi\u1ec7m gh\u1ebf Tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ban \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/6/bau-tu-tiep-tuc-giu-ghe-o-vpf.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean VPF \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n&nbsp;B\u1ea7u T\u00fa gi\u1eef gh\u1ebf \u1edf VPF trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng T\u00fa \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean H\u0110QT VPF th\u00f4ng qua. Sau bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp H\u0110QT di\u1ec5n ra s\u00e1ng nay (ng\u00e0y 10/4), 6/7 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea7u T\u00fa r\u1eddi \u0111i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, \u00f4ng Tr\u1ea7n M\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u0110QT VPF cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Anh T\u00fa xin r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed TG\u0110 VPF nh\u01b0ng H\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat, kh\u00f4ng vi ph\u1ea1m g\u00ec, t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111ang l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m, sao ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a H\u0110QT, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd cho anh T\u00fa r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed TG\u0110 VPF. 99% c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean H\u0110QT VPF kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd cho anh T\u00fa r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ch\u1ee9c danh TG\u0110&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean VPF ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn, b\u1ea7u T\u00fa c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong H\u0110QT \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p t\u00f4i r\u00fat. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 trong l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh t\u1edbi n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u00e0o t\u1ed1t, x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng, xin ph\u00e9p cho xem x\u00e9t chuy\u1ec3n giao ch\u1ee9c danh T\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a VPF.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh n\u00ean ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef ch\u1ee9c danh Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u0110QT th\u00ec s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n cho VPF. T\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o H\u0110QT, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e0i h\u01a1i cho 3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea7u T\u00fa ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1eef hai ch\u1ee9c v\u1ee5 cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i VPF v\u00e0 \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VFF ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB HAGL t\u1eebng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd r\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 kh\u1ecfi V-League 2018 n\u1ebfu b\u1ea7u T\u00fa v\u00e0o VFF.<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%;font-family:Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#081F2C;mso-fareast-language:KO\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"994","checkdouble":"183944"},{"date":"16:40 10/04","title":"B\u1ea7u T\u00fa: T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng lo chuy\u1ec7n ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng cho Duy M\u1ea1nh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/bau-tu-tang-tien-khong-lo-chuyen-phai-boi-thuong-cho-duy-manh.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding: